.cm SCRIPT REFERENCE BM
.SUBT Purpose
The BOTTOM MARGIN control word specifies the number of lines
which are to appear between the bottom of the
output page and the last line of ordinary or footnote text.
.SUBT Format
×
×  .BM          <6_×m×+m×-m>
×
.SUBT Usage
